Author: -onebyonebyone-
Text: Ok, I’m doing it! Thanks for the encouragement Haha I’m going to check it VSCO. I’ve never heard of it!

Author: androjennous
Text: Fuck it, do it, post a caption about how much fun you’re having (because you are!). If you’re extra nervous about how you look, find good light and work different angles and take a bunch until you find at least one or two that you’re confident with! If you feel like editing it, a litttttle bit of Facetune and VSCO go a long way to make you feel more comfortable :)
